How to create VPN
Create customer gateway VPC2-CG with EC2-site2 external IP
Create virtual private gateway - VPG
    attach to VPC1
Create site-to-stie VPN connection
    VPN connection with VPG and VPC2-CG
    static routing with other side network(this case for only one customer gateway)
Update route table to see VPC2
    route tables
    add the static route or
    route propagation to Yes
download configuration for your on side environment (Ex:on-premised or another AWS instance)
modify the configuration to make it fitable in the environment (change Tunnel ID, interface, and etc)

Need to use dynamic VPN and have two different customer gateway on two different IP